PN,41601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778602268
OL,3,CCouncil criticised for cutting
OL,4,Cautomatic school transport for some
OL,5,CSEND children
OL,7,F"It's not feasible. It doesn't cover
OL,8,Fthe cost and it won't work with our
OL,9,Flife," says Izabella Smykowska.
OL,11,F"The only option for me will be giving
OL,12,Fup my job. We have enquired with local
OL,13,Ftaxi companies about possible schools
OL,14,Ftrips, however the lowest quote was
OL,15,F#19,000 - and that's just for the
OL,16,Ftaxi."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778602268
OL,3,CCouncil criticised for cutting
OL,4,Cautomatic school transport for some
OL,5,CSEND children
OL,7,FMrs Smykowska is one of a number of
OL,8,Fparents in Kent who say the county
OL,9,Fcouncil has left them facing an
OL,10,Fimpossible choice about the future of
OL,11,Ftheir children's education.
OL,13,FThe authority has decided that it will
OL,14,Fno longer hire taxis or minibuses for
OL,15,Feligible students with special
OL,16,Feducational needs and disabilities
OL,17,F(SEND) over the age of 16 to get to
OL,18,Fschool.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778602268
OL,3,CCouncil criticised for cutting
OL,4,Cautomatic school transport for some
OL,5,CSEND children
OL,7,FFamilies will instead be given a
OL,8,Fpersonal budget to arrange transport
OL,9,Fthemselves.
OL,11,FBut for parents, including Mrs
OL,12,FSmykowska - whose 16-year-old
OL,13,Fdaughter, Tola, is non-verbal and has
OL,14,Fsevere learning disabilities - the
OL,15,Fmaths simply doesn't add up.
OL,17,FTola had for years travelled to school
OL,18,Fin a council contracted vehicle with a
OL,19,Fpersonal chaperone.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778602268
OL,3,CCouncil criticised for cutting
OL,4,Cautomatic school transport for some
OL,5,CSEND children
OL,7,FBut, when that comes to an end in
OL,8,FSeptember, Mrs Smykowska told ITV
OL,9,FMeridian that her family will need to
OL,10,Fplug a #14,000 shortfall to get her
OL,11,Fdaughter to school.
OL,13,FIt's a dilemma that Tola's father,
OL,14,FMichael Smykowska, said they cannot
OL,15,Fafford.
OL,17,F"Put it very simply we might not be
OL,18,Fable to pay the mortgage or bills
OL,19,Fbecause, like many other households,
OL,20,Fwe rely on two incomes," he said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778602268
OL,3,CCouncil criticised for cutting
OL,4,Cautomatic school transport for some
OL,5,CSEND children
OL,7,F"We might have to consider claiming
OL,8,Fbenefits, which we don't want to.
OL,9,FWe've worked all our lives and we want
OL,10,Fto work."
OL,12,FMr Smykowska added: "We are trying to
OL,13,Flead our lives as best we can and this
OL,14,Fchange is cutting us completely."
OL,16,FKent County Council (KCC) said in a
OL,17,Fstatement that it is not legally
OL,18,Fobliged to provide "automatic
OL,19,Ftransport" to children after they turn
OL,20,F16.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778602268
OL,3,CCouncil criticised for cutting
OL,4,Cautomatic school transport for some
OL,5,CSEND children
OL,7,FIt added the changes will help "ensure
OL,8,Fsupport remains fair, proportionate
OL,9,Fand sustainable".
OL,11,F"Historically, KCC has been able to
OL,12,Foffer a very generous discretionary
OL,13,Fpackage for some adult learners,
OL,14,Fparticularly those with SEND and
OL,15,FEducation, Health and Care Plans,
OL,16,Fmeaning their transport often
OL,17,Fcontinued much as it had before 16,"
OL,18,Fthe statement read.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778602268
OL,3,CCouncil criticised for cutting
OL,4,Cautomatic school transport for some
OL,5,CSEND children
OL,7,F"That level of support was never
OL,8,Funiversal, and most Adult Learners -
OL,9,Fincluding many with SEND - already
OL,10,Fmake their own travel arrangements.
OL,12,F"What has changed is how support is
OL,13,Fprovided. For sixth form age students,
OL,14,Fthey will now be offered a personal
OL,15,Ftransport budget rather than having
OL,16,Ftransport automatically arranged.
OL,18,F"Adult learners are now asked to first
OL,19,Fseek help from their college or
OL,20,Ftraining provider through the 16`19
OL,21,Fbursary fund.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778602268
OL,3,CCouncil criticised for cutting
OL,4,Cautomatic school transport for some
OL,5,CSEND children
OL,7,F"If this support is not enough, KCC
OL,8,Fmay then consider a mileage payment,
OL,9,Fgiving families greater flexibility
OL,10,Fand control.
OL,12,F"Where an individual has the highest
OL,13,Flevel of need, specialist transport
OL,14,Fcan still be requested and will be
OL,15,Fprovided where this is assessed as
OL,16,Fnecessary.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778602268
OL,3,CCouncil criticised for cutting
OL,4,Cautomatic school transport for some
OL,5,CSEND children
OL,7,F"All transport decisions are subject
OL,8,Fto a statutory twostage appeals
OL,9,Fprocess, ensuring families are able to
OL,10,Fchallenge decisions and have their
OL,11,Findividual circumstances fully
OL,12,Fconsidered.
OL,14,F"These proposals were consulted on
OL,15,Fpublicly between January and March
OL,16,F2025, with feedback carefully
OL,17,Fconsidered."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
